snippet.title: CJ's Elephant Antics Longplay (Amiga) [4K]
snippet.description:
Follow me on Twitter @ https://twitter.com/Al82_Retro
Get Great Retro Scene News @ http://www.vintageisthenewold.com
Developed by Genesis Software and published by Codemasters in 1991

Pretty good Amiga conversion of the C64 classic, although little else. It's decent-enough fun for what it is, but whereas the C64 version offered great value for money, the same couldn't have been said for this.

Chapters
00:00 (music by Allister Brimble)
02:26 Level 1: France (music by Allister Brimble)
06:28 Level 2: Switzerland (music by Allister Brimble)
10:38 Level 3: Egypt (music by Allister Brimble)
16:18 Level 4: Africa (music by Allister Brimble)
19:42 Ending (music by Allister Brimble)
